      <p>Welcome to <strong><%=appName%></strong>, a cutting-edge medical application designed to revolutionize the way healthcare professionals manage patient data. At <strong><%=appName%></strong>, we're dedicated to providing an intuitive and secure platform for doctors and NHS staff to streamline their workflow and enhance patient care.</p>
      
