          <li><strong>Intuitive Interface:</strong> Designed with user experience in mind, our platform offers a user-friendly interface that minimizes learning curves and maximizes productivity.</li>
          <li><strong>Advanced Search Functionality:</strong> Quickly locate patient records with powerful search capabilities, allowing medical professionals to retrieve relevant information with ease.</li>
      </ul>
      
